    "headline": "The org grows up: first COO, first People function",
    "body": "With 28 people and a growing sense that informal coordination is straining, Finch makes two pivotal hires: Jordan Reeve as COO and Adrienne Cole as Head of People. The Growth Engineering team gets its first dedicated manager in Leo Carvalho. Emma Sinclair (People Ops) exits after one year \u2014 an early warning sign about onboarding gaps.",
